<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Invitation to Join a Business</title>
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-width: 100%;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            background-color: #fafafa;
            color: #222;
        }
        a {
            color: #000;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.25;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        p {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .email-header {
            background-color: #3858F8;
            padding: 24px;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .email-body {
            padding: 24px;
            background-color: #fff;
        }
        .email-footer {
            background-color: #f6f6f6;
            padding: 24px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #3858F8;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>You're Invited to Join <%= businessName %></h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Hello,</p>
            <p>
                You have been invited to join the business 
                <strong><%= businessName %></strong> with the role of 
                <strong><%= role %></strong> on Academix.
            </p>
            <p>
                To get started, please create your account and accept this invitation by clicking the button below.
            </p>
            <p style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="<%= registerLink %>" class="button">Go to create account</a>
            </p>
            <p>
                This invitation link will expire in 7 days. If you did not expect this invitation, you can ignore this email.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>
                If you have any questions, feel free to contact us at 
                <a href="mailto:support@academix.com">support@academix.com</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
